layouts.Name: Rollin Ridge A Pool Layout
layouts.Notes:
The official end of the tee pad is the line.  You cannot step on or over the line.  
Out of Bounds (806.02) - Marked by WHITE line. This applies to all marked OB areas even if they are not mentioned explicitly on a specific hole. 					
Relief Area (806.04) - Marked by PINK line.					
Casual Area (806.03) - Marked by RED line.					
Mandatory (804.01) - Restricted plane marked by marked object and ORANGE line.
